name: Let The Sea Set You Free
description: Experience the very best of the Whitsundays aboard a premium and beloved day tour. This fast power catamaran promises a thrilling ride, perfect for adventure seekers looking to explore the natural beauty of the Whitsundays. Cruise at a speedy 25 knots, allowing you to maximize your time visiting North and South Whitehaven Beach, snorkeling in the vibrant fringing reefs of the Great Barrier Reef Marine Park, and taking in breathtaking views from Hill Inlet Lookout.
includes:
Buffet lunch
Wetsuits
Snorkel gear
Paddleboards
highlights:
Fast power catamaran ride in the Whitsundays
Visit North and South Whitehaven Beach
Snorkel in the Great Barrier Reef Marine Park
Hill Inlet Lookout for stunning views
Cruise at 25 knots for maximum exploration time
price_tiers: Adult: $230 AUD per Person | Child (2-14 years): $199 AUD per Person | Family (2A + 2C): $760 AUD per Family
ideal_for: Adventure seekers, nature lovers, and those looking to experience the Whitsundays in a day.
whats_extra: ['$20 per adult and $10 per child surcharge applies to all tickets on public holidays.', 'Please see our FAQs page for more information on which dates this surcharge applies to.']
